Q. Check if Array Is Sorted and Rotated

Explanation: nums = [3,4,5,1,2]  - Iterate thorugh array, if the count of this occurance ( first element is bigger than the second element ) is greater than 1 , then False.     
             nums[i]>nums[(i+1)%n] - condition



class Solution {
    public boolean check(int[] nums) {
        int n=nums.length;
        int count=0;
        for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
            if(nums[i]>nums[(i+1)%n]){
                count++;
            }
        }
        if(count>1){
            return false;
        }
        else{
            return true;
        }
    }
}

